        "id": 5010
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-10-12T16:50:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "These types don\u0027t look right to me.  Reading https://developer.android.com/ndk/reference/trace_8h.html, I think you want to type:\n\nstatic void (*ATrace_beginSection)(const char*) \u003d nullptr;\nstatic void (*ATrace_endSection)()              \u003d nullptr;\nstatic bool (*ATrace_isEnabled)()               \u003d nullptr;",
      "revId": "b211b4076138598ffad08376326e2301ce36c2bc",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "key": {
